[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    519[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    520[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **External Resources:**
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    521[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - [MIMIC-IV-ED on PhysioNet](https://physionet.org/content/mimic-iv-ed/): De-identified ED visit data from a Boston academic medical center, suitable for prototyping ED forecasting models with credentialed access
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    522[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - [CDC FluView](https://www.cdc.gov/flu/weekly/index.htm): National and regional influenza surveillance data, a key exogenous input for respiratory-season ED forecasting
